snippet.title: Lost Judgment: The Kaito Files - Official Primal Focus Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the trailer to see Kaito's Primal Focus ability in action from Lost Judgment's upcoming story expansion, The Kaito Files. Kaito's Primal Focus allows the character to literally sniff out clues, identify suspects, and crack the case.

The Kaito Files story expansion for Lost Judgment launches on PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, Xbox Series X/S, and Xbox One on March 28, 2022.

#GameTrailers
